Package org.cruk.genologics.api.jaxb

Classes to aid the JAXB object mapping process.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
JaxbMarshallingTool Tool to help debugging: a short cut for marshalling an object to a string.
JaxbUnmarshallingAspect Aspect that wraps the unmarshalling of responses from the Genologics API.
KnownNamespacePrefixMatcher Implementation of the internal Sun JAXB NamespacePrefixMapper to make sure the XML documents created from JAXB have user friendly name spaces in their headers.
LongTimestampAdapter Adapter for those dates that are exchanged with the API in the long timestamp format.
URIAdapter Removes the "state" parameter from the query part of a URI string before converting to a URI object, or when converting back.
